              "title": "Choose Your Event-Day Intention",
              "aha": "Let your body’s reality choose the intention, not a generic routine.",
              "action": "Use the Intention Selection Framework to rate your current energy level, stress level, and body stiffness on a 1–5 scale. Based on your scores, circle the recommended intention (energize, calm, or mobilize) and write one sentence describing what you need most before your upcoming event.",
