              "aha": "Five intention-matched poses with steady breath beat ten minutes of random stretching.",
              "action": "Follow the Pre-Event Warm-Up Flow Card that matches your chosen intention. Perform each pose for five breaths, applying the alignment cues from Step 2. After the flow, record which poses felt best and note any modifications you used (e.g., bent knees in Forward Fold for tight hamstrings, fists on the floor instead of flat palms for wrist sensitivity).",
              "tool": "Pre-Event Warm-Up Flow Card: a set of three illustrated flow sequences (one per intention) with five to six poses each, breath count per pose, alignment reminders, and a modification sidebar for tight hips, stiff shoulders, and wrist sensitivity."
